## **Summary of Recommendations**

| Priority | Issue | Fix |
|----------|-------|-----|
| 🔴 CRITICAL | No Authentication | Add JWT/OAuth authentication |
| 🟠 HIGH | No Input Validation | Use express-validator |
| 🟠 HIGH | Missing Security Headers | Use helmet middleware |
| 🟠 HIGH | No CORS Config | Configure CORS properly |
| 🟠 HIGH | No Rate Limiting | Add express-rate-limit |
| 🟠 HIGH | Hardcoded Data | Use environment variables |
| 🟡 MEDIUM | No Error Handling | Add global error handler |
| 🟡 MEDIUM | No HTTPS Enforcement | Redirect HTTP to HTTPS |
| 🟡 MEDIUM | No Body Limits | Configure parser limits |
